  /* Preview frame mirrors the featured hero's portrait crop; drag the image to
     set the focal point. The dashed guide shows the smaller article-card crop. */
  /* The frame is the featured hero's exact crop shape (~2.2:1 at desktop), so
     what you frame here is what the hero shows. A tall image overflows
     top/bottom; pan up/down to pick the crop. The dashed guide marks where a
     small (non-hero) card — a wider, shorter shape — actually lands. */
  .cover-preview {
